golang-blackfriday (1.5.2+git20200218.41c5fcc-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version 1.5.2+git20200218.41c5fcc
  * Set debian/watch to track git HEAD
  * Remove dependency on golang-github-shurcool-sanitized-anchor-name-dev.
    Upstream now includes a copy of SanitizedAnchorName inside blackfriday,
    see https://github.com/russross/blackfriday/pull/352
